{"tid":2134470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔需要灰心 真正屬於香港人既選舉一早已經舉行左","createTime":"2020-07-31T17:32:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T18:03:10.000Z","uid":41411,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e7f634fc577bf0a17da870a28e0f12bb7eef324e","tid":2134470,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:32:57.000Z","msg":"係7月12日 有60萬真香港人已經投左佢地神聖既一票<br />\n7月12日既選舉 係屬於香港人公平公開公正既選舉<br />\n儘管我地香港人而家已經失去左被選舉權同選舉權，我地都唔應該灰心<br />\n你笑我打飛機都好，我地生於依個時代 我地已經盡左我地既努力<br />\n之後條路會係點 我同你都唔會預計到 包括個政府<br />\n<br />\n但有一樣野我好肯定，歷史一定會為我地做一個見證<br />\n就算港共今日DQ晒我地既參選人<br />\n但歷史都會記載住我地係曾經有一場盛大既選舉"},{"pid":"0f53a6294349f390a38a79fc02b48094f104dcca","tid":2134470,"uid":86747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:47:43.000Z","msg":"真，其實呢個選舉就係民意展現，贏咗嘅人好好諗下點樣善用挾住民意做更多嘅嘢"},{"pid":"39a138ff0b8e8cb8eebb36bdaa67f3ca1383c69e","tid":2134470,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:52:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da21a7e2f8a942a5c05b0746a66579caac7f882","tid":2134470,"uid":92299,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:56:48.000Z","msg":"個個都淨係識用選票打飛機，一啲勇武反抗嘅心都冇，唔怪之得林鄭到今時今日都仲可以咁撚臭寸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87dec769600fb0d7341f812208cce32eb5d068ba","tid":2134470,"uid":100016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:57:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1e5a16b9760532dc103db6b99592ac0251c88f5","tid":2134470,"uid":92299,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87dec769600fb0d7341f812208cce32eb5d068ba","tid":2134470,"uid":100016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:57:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T18:03:10.000Z","msg":"投個票就話盡咗